001 - Variables to be analyzed to contract the best Financial Strategy

Por Preload - 04-07-2017

A correct Financial Strategy will determine the success of the business so it is very important to correctly evaluate all the variables involved.
In this presentation are mentioned, in addition to the typical financial variables, those variables that are mainly related to the Mobile Network Infrastructure activity.
In order to determine the best financial Strategy to adopt, it is very important to define the minimum and maximum limits of these variables among which the Company can feel safe and comfortable to work.
